ry, but he may just be the lesser of the two evils. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://p075.ezboard.com/bascension10244.showUserPublicProfile?gid=neeeeeedra>Neeeeeedra</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 44<br> <font color=#333333>(6/7/04 9:44 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://p075.ezboard.com/fascension10244frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2705.topic&index=66>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> !</span><hr size=1> www.scaryjohnkerry.com/wmd.htm <br>
